Package com.im.njams.sdk.communication.fragments

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChunkedMessage
    Used for collecting message chunks that form a complete message only when all chunks arrived.
    GenericChunkAssembly<T>
    Collects and merges messages that are split into several chunks.
    See GenericChunkAssembly.resolve(Object) for details.
    HttpSseChunkAssembly
    HTTP server sent events implementation working on MessageEvent messages.
    JMSChunkAssembly
    JMS implementation working on TextMessage messages.
    KafkaChunkAssembly
    Kafka implementation working on ConsumerRecord messages.
    RawMessage
    Immutable container for messages build of headers and message body.
    SplitSupport
    Splits large messages according to the configuration setting NjamsSettings.PROPERTY_MAX_MESSAGE_SIZE or using a technical size limit caused by the used transport implementation.
    SplitSupport.Range
    Simple immutable container for two int values defining a from/to range.
